.Dd 2015-10-08
.Dt NOHUP 1
.Os sbase
.Sh NAME
.Nm nohup
.Nd run command immune to hangups
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar cmd
.Op Ar arg ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
runs
.Ar cmd
with the
.Em HUP
signal set to be ignored.
.Pp
If stdout is a terminal, it is appended to
.Em nohup.out
in the current working directory.
If stderr is a terminal, it is redirected to stdout.
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It 0
.Ar cmd
executed successfully.
.It 1
Internal error.
.It 126
.Ar cmd
was found but could not be executed.
.It 127
.Ar cmd
could not be found.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr signal 7
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Nm
utility is compliant with the
.St -p1003.1-2013
specification.
